<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Raja Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #333;
        }
        nav a {
            padding: 14px 20px;
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }
        main {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 80%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    Welcome to Raja's Website
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#home">Home</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<main>
    <h1>Main Content Area</h1>
    <p>This is where your main content will go. You can add more sections, images, or anything you need to create a compelling webpage.</p>
</main>

<footer>
    &copy; 2024 Raja's Website. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
